{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/ms-build와-nu-get","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"왜-msbuild-왜-nuget\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%99%9C-msbuild-%EC%99%9C-nuget\" aria-label=\"왜 msbuild 왜 nuget permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>왜 MSBuild? 왜 NuGet?</h1>\n<p>마이크로소프트웨어 관련 개발은 비주얼 스튜디오를 사용하여 개발을 진행하게 된다. IDE 위에서 참조 라이브러리를 손으로 얹거나 NuGet Package Manager를 통해 패키지를 관리하고, Debug, Release로 타겟을 정해여 빌드 후 Publish 메뉴로 배포까지 할 수 있다.\n로컬 머신에서 빌드 후 테스트 서버와 운영 서버에 배포할 수도 있겠지만, 단계가 늘어감에 따라 소스만 가지고 빌드를 따로 진행해야 할 필요가 있 </p>\n<p>CI/CDㄹ하지만 CI/CD환경을 구성하려면 빌드 스크립트를 짜올려야 한다. IDE가 하는 일을 내가 </p>\n<h2 id=\"nuget\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nuget\" aria-label=\"nuget permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nuget</h2>\n<h3 id=\"기본-명령\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9\" aria-label=\"기본 명령 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기본 명령</h3>\n<p>기본 명령은 다음과 같다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nuget.exe restore project.sln</code></pre></div>\n<p>restore는 정의된 프로젝트의 </p>\n<h2 id=\"msbuild\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#msbuild\" aria-label=\"msbuild permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MSBuild</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">msbuild.exe project.csproj</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"robocopy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#robocopy\" aria-label=\"robocopy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>robocopy</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">robocopy</code></pre></div>\n<p>robocopy를 돌리면 정상적으로 카피가 끝나면 exit code로 1을 던진다. gitlab은 CI/CD 동작 판단에 unix exit code를 사용하는데, 1은 general error이다. 즉, 카피가 정상적으로 이루어지면 error가 뜨면서 build failed가 올라온다.\nrobocopy의 exit code중 0(0x00), 1(0x01), 2(0x10), 4(0x100)는 카피가 정상종료되었다고 볼 수 있으므로 8미만(0x111)의 값이 오면 0으로 강제 설정하여 빌드를 성공으로 만들 수 있다.\n이를 배포 스크립트에 반영해보면,</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(robocopy /mir source dest /w:1 /r:1); if( $lastexitcode -lt 8 ) { $lastexitcode = 0 }</code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 변경하고 실행해보면 정상적으로 build가 pass됨을 알 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"단일-솔루션-복수-프로젝트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A8%EC%9D%BC-%EC%86%94%EB%A3%A8%EC%85%98-%EB%B3%B5%EC%88%98-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"단일 솔루션 복수 프로젝트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>단일 솔루션, 복수 프로젝트</h2>\n<p>nuget package 위치가 꼬인다.\n같이 참조가 걸려있더라도 쓰는게 좋은 것 같기도하고.</p>\n<h1 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>[펌]실전! 지속적인 통합 10편: MSBuild 따라하기 : <a href=\"https://megustaria.tistory.com/3\">https://megustaria.tistory.com/3</a></li>\n<li>NuGet : <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/nuget/what-is-nuget\">https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/nuget/what-is-nuget</a></li>\n<li>Stop gitlab runner to not remove a directory : <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42948062/stop-gitlab-runner-to-not-remove-a-directory\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42948062/stop-gitlab-runner-to-not-remove-a-directory</a></li>\n<li>Specify project file of a solution using msbuild : <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13915636/specify-project-file-of-a-solution-using-msbuild\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13915636/specify-project-file-of-a-solution-using-msbuild</a></li>\n<li>Robocopy exit alwsy with status code 1 and hence failing the job even if with all success : <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/31956\">https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/31956</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.kldp.org/HOWTO/html/Adv-Bash-Scr-HOWTO/exitcodes.html\">https://wiki.kldp.org/HOWTO/html/Adv-Bash-Scr-HOWTO/exitcodes.html</a></li>\n<li>How to stop robocopy from exiting the build? : <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/44504795/how-to-stop-robocopy-from-exiting-the-build\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/44504795/how-to-stop-robocopy-from-exiting-the-build</a></li>\n<li>robocopy exit codes : <a href=\"https://ss64.com/nt/robocopy-exit.html\">https://ss64.com/nt/robocopy-exit.html</a></li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"왜 MSBuild? 왜 NuGet? 마이크로소프트웨어 관련 개발은 비주얼 스튜디오를 사용하여 개발을 진행하게 된다. IDE 위에서 참조 라이브러리를 손으로 얹거나 NuGet Package Manager를 통해 패키지를 관리하고, Debug…","frontmatter":{"title":"MSBuild와 NuGet","cover":"sunset-2173918_1920.jpg","date":"2020-05-25","category":"","tags":["MSBuild","NuGet","C3"]},"fields":{"slug":"/ms-build와-nu-get","date":"2020-05-24T15:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ms-build와-nu-get","nexttitle":"vCenter Server for Windows to vCenter Server Appliance","nextslug":"/v-center-server-for-windows-to-v-center-server-appliance","prevtitle":"Tomcat 업데이트(9.0.16->9.0.35)","prevslug":"/tomcat-업데이트-9-0-16-9-0-35"}}}